<i>adverb</i>: 슬슬 [슬슬], 살살 [살살] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>슬슬 [슬슬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알아차리지 못하게 천천히 조용하게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly and quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>2. imperceptibly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 설탕 등이 모르는 사이에 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing snow, sugar, etc., melting away before one knows.</dd><br>
<dd>3. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>세지 않게 만지거나 문지르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of touching or rubbing something tenderly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. adroitly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 드러나지 않게 은근히 설득하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of persuading someone indirectly so that one's intention is not revealed.</dd><br>
<dd>5. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍고 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing lightly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. gently</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 눈웃음을 치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling with one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. slowly</dd><br>
<dd>서두르지 않고 천천히 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly, not hastening.</dd><br>
<dd>8. effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘들이지 않고 쉽게 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of doing something easily without much effort.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>살살 [살살]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알아차리지 못하게 천천히 조용하게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of acting slowly and quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>2. imperceptibly; softly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 설탕 등이 모르는 사이에 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of snow, sugar, etc., melting away before one knows.</dd><br>
<dd>3. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>세지 않게 만지거나 문지르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of touching or rubbing something tenderly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. adroitly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 드러나지 않게 은근히 설득하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of persuading someone indirectly so that one's intention is not revealed.</dd><br>
<dd>5. gently</dd><br>
<dd>바람이 가볍고 부드럽게 부는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the wind blowing lightly and softly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. gently</dd><br>
<dd>가볍게 눈웃음을 치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of smiling with one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. smoothly</dd><br>
<dd>얽힌 실 등이 잘 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of tangled thread, etc., disentangling easily.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>